## System Manifest — Read Before Every Change

Before modifying any code, read `docs/system-manifest.yaml`:
- The `cross_cutting` section lists your project's conventions that apply to all code
- The domain entry for the area you're modifying lists its specific conventions + facade APIs
- Follow every convention listed. If unsure whether a convention applies, it applies.

## Cross-Cutting Conventions (enforced on ALL code)

